了终身伤害，一辈子都没有办法再正常生活，希望能够严惩凶手。5 日，律师姚克枫称，已就该案组建律师团队，他认为施暴者已经涉嫌故意杀人，无论最终是故意伤害致人重伤，还是说故意杀人未遂，都建议重判施暴者。谢女士与贺某某相识 3 年、结婚 2 年，怀孕后其被贺某某家暴多达 16 次。据多家媒体报道，谢女士曾遭遇扇巴掌、用手机扇脸、拖拽到小区树林殴打等暴力行为，致使谢女士肋骨骨折、十二指肠被污染、小肠梗阻肾、胰、肺等内脏受到不同程度损伤。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-cd1ecaba877247faaa894c43e11dd0ce_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "340 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/610619293"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ijuf86NOuo4FBEAMaCDk3OTc0MDM0IKKlmKUGMAA4ugJAA3IJNjEwNjE5MjkzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1688691230.458979", "card_id": "Q_602728740", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 167}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "不沉迷游戏和热爱游戏可能并存吗？如果可以，是如何做到的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-efcd04cb41be0b4a642ea37ad6cafcb6_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/602728740"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ijuf86NOuo4FBEAMaCDk2MjIwMTAyIImItqMGMAA49gFABHIJNjAyNzI4NzQweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1688691230.459211", "card_id": "Q_385026167", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 114}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么优秀员工往往最先离职？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "imag